         ]
      },
      {
         "id": "SECTION_andes",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><h3>Andean numerical systems</h3><h4>Quipus</h4>The quipu system is an ancient method of counting, likely originating in the sacred city of Caral, Peru (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('720f6dfd-4b86-4e07-a887-1010e1041a4d'); return false;\">Ruta Caral, <htdate0></a> ; <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('03c3743c-d268-4730-ba8e-d36b5c49e781'); return false;\">Youtube - Caral Perú Oficial, <htdate1></a> ; <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('a7abe0b7-b3bf-44d6-ab4d-e7d32d2586ad'); return false;\">Moras, Roberto., <htdate2></a>):</p><p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgQuipuPanel\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgQuipuPanel', '0%')\" src=\"images/Caral/QuipuPanel.png\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figure 2</b>: Panel at the Caral archaeological site, © ZonaArqueólogicaCaral (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('720f6dfd-4b86-4e07-a887-1010e1041a4d'); return false;\">Ruta Caral, <htdate3></a> ; <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('03c3743c-d268-4730-ba8e-d36b5c49e781'); return false;\">Youtube - Caral Perú Oficial, <htdate4></a>). Photo taken on <htdate5>, during a visit to the archaeological site of Caral.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": [
                  {
                     "type": "gregory",
                     "year": "2024",
                     "month": "-1",
                     "day": "-1"
                  },
                  {
                     "type": "gregory",
                     "year": "2024",
                     "month": "-1",
                     "day": "-1"
                  },
                  {
                     "type": "gregory",
                     "year": "2024",
                     "month": "-1",
                     "day": "-1"
                  },
                  {
                     "type": "gregory",
                     "year": "2024",
